data.description:
This 4 bedroom pool home has been professionally designed and renovated. No detail has been overlooked with new cabinets, counters, floors, appliances, paint, tile and more. Newly re-piped with all new electrical and re-insulation. Energy efficient with Solar panels and new LED light fixtures. Features include dual primary suites, large kitchen island with open concept floor plan, den, direct access laundry room, covered parking and newly paved pool-side covered patio. 
Situated on a large corner lot near the Phoenix Mountains Preserve with access to miles of hiking and biking from the Wind Rock Trail head. Quick access to the 51 freeway and central to TPC, Phoenix Open, Mayo Clinic, Phoenix Sky Harbor International Airport, amazing restaurants, shopping and stadiums. NO HOA.
